{"type":"message","id":"a6f30061","parentId":"7e3d3040","timestamp":"2026-03-07T14:02:38.177Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cc89b732e132d5566befff839f63c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# GitHub Star 数量对比报告（2026年3月）\n\n## OpenClaw\n- **Star 数量**: 250,000+\n- **排名**: GitHub 最受欢迎的开源项目\n- **增长趋势**: 2025年11月发布后迅速增长，60天内达到25万星标\n\n## Linux\n- **Star 数量**: 218,000\n- **排名**: 被 OpenClaw 超越，现为第14名\n\n## Python\n- **Star 数量**:\n  - `EbookFoundation/free-programming-books`: 380,000+\n  - `transformers` (Hugging Face): 157,000+\n  - `Auto-GPT`: 182,000+\n\n## React\n- **Star 数量**: 203,000\n- **排名**: OpenClaw 超越后，排名有所下降\n\n### 结论\nOpenClaw 在2026年3月成为 GitHub 上最受欢迎的开源项目，超越了 React、Linux 和其他知名项目，展示了其在 AI 和开源社区中的强大影响力。"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772892158166}}
{"type":"message","id":"d359fc49","parentId":"a6f30061","timestamp":"2026-03-07T14:02:50.932Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已读取数据文件，稍后将生成可视化图表。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cc89b819160accbd3e6c3e81063d2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/writer/github_stars.py","content":"import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n\n# Data extracted from research_report.md\nprojects = [\"OpenClaw\", \"Linux\", \"Python (EbookFoundation)\", \"Python (Transformers)\", \"Python (Auto-GPT)\", \"React\"]\nstars = [250000, 218000, 380000, 157000, 182000, 203000]\n\n# Creating the bar plot\nplt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))\nplt.bar(projects, stars, color=['blue', 'green', 'orange', 'orange', 'orange', 'red'])\n\n# Adding titles and labels\nplt.title(\"GitHub Star 数量对比 (2026年3月)\", fontsize=14)\nplt.xlabel(\"项目名称\", fontsize=12)\nplt.ylabel(\"Star 数量\", fontsize=12)\nplt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')\n\n# Displaying the plot\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.savefig(\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/writer/github_stars.png\")\nplt.show()"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openai","model":"deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3","usage":{"input":4916,"output":291,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":5207,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772892158191}}
